&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with operations, technology, and finance teams to validate findings and secure alignment on prioritization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish baseline metrics and KPIs to measure the impact of AI initiatives over time&lt;/li&gt;
