&lt;p&gt;AdvancedMD is a unified cloud suite of medical office software hosted on Amazon Web Services/AWS including practice management, electronic health records, and patient engagement, and offers managed medical billing services for independent practices.&amp;nbsp;AdvancedMD serves an expansive national footprint of 65,000 practitioners across 14,000 practices and 900 independent medical billing companies. 8.8M insurance claims are processed every month on the&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.advancedmd.com/company/media-coverage/&quot;&gt;AdvancedMD billing&lt;/a&gt; platform!&lt;/p&gt;
